description: This hall of fame Cooter purrs with a rating of 59, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 472, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Stringalong for East, 8 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [472 Votes, Hall of Fame]
